E等视频<br /> * <strong>限制流量，不适合电脑使用</strong> (只使用手机，流量足够。)<br /> * 在线购买，立刻自动开通帐号</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\"><strong><span>淘宝地址：<a href=\"http://aa.cx/vpna\">http://aa.cx/vpna</a></span></strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>VPN Plan B 有效期1年 vpn_plan_B for 1 year</td>\n<td>  <img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://www.paypal.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif\" width=\"1\" /> </td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\">* 同时支持 PPTP 与 L2TP 协议<br /> * <strong>可同时使用2个设备： 手机+电脑</strong><br /> * 不限制流量<br /> * 在线购买，立刻自动开通帐号</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\"><span><strong>淘宝地址：<a href=\"http://aa.cx/vpnb\">http://aa.cx/vpnb</a></strong></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>VPN Plan C 有效期1年 vpn_plan_C for 1 year</td>\n<td>  <img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://www.paypal.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif\" width=\"1\" /> </td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\">* 同时支持 PPTP 与 L2TP 协议<br /> * 支持同时使用2个设备： 手机+电脑<br /> * <strong>独立IP地址，可玩游戏</strong><br /> * 不限制流量<br /> * 在线购买，立刻自动开通帐号 </p>\n<p><strong><span>淘宝地址：<a href=\"http://aa.cx/vpnc\">http://aa.cx/vpnc</a></span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><strong><span>购买方法</span></strong></p>\n<p><span><span><span><span>直接支付相应金额到我的支付宝账户或者paypal账户</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span><span><strong><a href=\"mailto:jinwei1014@gmail.com\">jinwei1014@gmail.com</a></strong></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span><span>之后发邮件到我的Gmail告知交易号和购买的套餐计划。</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span><span>为了保障交易安全，请尽量使用Gmail。</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><strong><span>测试帐号</span></strong></p>\n<p>需要VPN测试帐号的(适用于IPHONE, ANDRIOD等智能手机），请发邮件给 <strong><a href=\"http://eevpn.com\">eevpn.com</a></strong><strong>@<a href=\"http://gmail.com\">gmail.com</a></strong> 标题：VPN TEST</p>\n<p><strong><span><span><span>使用方法</span></span></span></strong></p>\n<p>VPN的使用方法其实很简单，这里还是用图文并茂的方式给大家做个详细的教程吧，以免。。。。</p>\n<p>首先是<span>IPHONE</span>平台的设置方式：</p>\n<p>1. 点击设置</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/iPhone_1.jpg\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"502\" src=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/iPhone_1.jpg\" title=\"iPhone_1\" width=\"356\" /></a></p>\n<p>2. 选择通用</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/iPhone_2.jpg\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"500\" src=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/iPhone_2.jpg\" title=\"iPhone_2\" width=\"343\" /></a></p>\n<p>3. 选择网络</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/iPhone_3.jpg\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"482\" src=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/iPhone_3.jpg\" title=\"iPhone_3\" width=\"325\" /></a></p>\n<p>4. 选择VPN</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/iPhone_4.jpg\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"488\" src=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/iPhone_4.jpg\" title=\"iPhone_4\" width=\"326\" /></a></p>\n<p>5. 添加VPN设置</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/iPhone_5.jpg\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"496\" src=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/iPhone_5.jpg\" title=\"iPhone_5\" width=\"341\" /></a></p>\n<p>6. 设置L2DP，把你购买的VPN服务器，账户，密码，密匙分别填入对应的栏目内，其它选项保持不变。然后点击右上角的储存。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/L2DP.jpg\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"480\" src=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/L2DP.jpg\" title=\"L2DP\" width=\"318\" /></a></p>\n<p>7. PPTP的VPN设置，最好记得点击右上角的存储按钮。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/iPhone_6.jpg\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"478\" src=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/iPhone_6.jpg\" title=\"iPhone_6\" width=\"320\" /></a></p>\n<p>8. 设置完成，点击VPN按钮会提示正在连接，成功之后，就。。。。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/iPhone_7.jpg\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"481\" src=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/iPhone_7.jpg\" title=\"iPhone_7\" width=\"323\" /></a></p>\n<p>下面介绍<span>ANDROID</span>系统的VPN设置方法：</p>\n<p>1. 进入settings</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/1.png\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"480\" src=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/1.png\" title=\"1\" width=\"320\" /></a></p>\n<p>2. 选择wireless &#038; networks</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/2.png\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"480\" src=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/2.png\" title=\"2\" width=\"320\" /></a></p>\n<p>3. 选择VPN settings</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/3.png\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"480\" src=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/3.png\" title=\"3\" width=\"320\" /></a></p>\n<p>4. 设置VPN Name，这个可以随便写</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/4.png\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"480\" src=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/4.png\" title=\"4\" width=\"320\" /></a></p>\n<p>5. 输入购买的VPN的服务器名</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/5.png\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"480\" src=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/5.png\" title=\"5\" width=\"320\" /></a></p>\n<p>6. 然后点击保存</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/6.png\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"480\" src=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/6.png\" title=\"6\" width=\"320\" /></a></p>\n<p>7. 然后点击之前设置的VPN名字，在弹出的窗口输入账户和密码并勾选记住用户名和密码。设置完成。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/8.png\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"480\" src=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/8.png\" title=\"8\" width=\"320\" /></a></p>\n<p>然后是<span>WINDOWS</span>平台的VPN设置：</p>\n<p>1. 在系统的桌面上找到网上邻居</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/image001.png\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"63\" src=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/image001.png\" title=\"image001\" width=\"59\" /></a></p>\n<p>2. 鼠标右键点击网上邻居点击“属性”</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/image003.png\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"189\" src=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/image003.png\" title=\"image003\" width=\"164\" /></a></p>\n<p>3. 网络任务里点击“单击创建一个新的连接”</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/image005.png\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"119\" src=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/image005.png\" title=\"image005\" width=\"185\" /></a></p>\n<p>4. 下一步</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/image007.png\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"373\" src=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/image007.png\" title=\"image007\" width=\"501\" /></a></p>\n<p>5. 选择“连接到我的工作场所的网络”下一步</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/image009.png\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"370\" src=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/image009.png\" title=\"image009\" width=\"498\" /></a></p>\n<p>6．选择“虚拟专用网络连接”下一步</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/image011.png\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"378\" src=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/image011.png\" title=\"image011\" width=\"501\" /></a></p>\n<p>7. 下一步,公司名可以留空。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/image013.png\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"377\" src=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/image013.png\" title=\"image013\" width=\"500\" /></a></p>\n<p>8. 注意：这里如果选择“不拨初始连接”</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/image015.png\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"378\" src=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/image015.png\" title=\"image015\" width=\"498\" /></a></p>\n<p>9.输入公司VPN地址“218.241.238.141”下一步</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/image017.png\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"377\" src=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/image017.png\" title=\"image017\" width=\"501\" /></a></p>\n<p>10.“在我的桌面上添加一个到此连接的快捷方式”前面打上√完成</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/image019.png\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"377\" src=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/image019.png\" title=\"image019\" width=\"500\" /></a></p>\n<p>11. 在桌面上双击刚才建立的虚拟私人网络连接，在连接窗口输入账号和密码，点击连接就可以了。如果出现错误，直接忽略。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/b7f9a09a7e0972b561507406efeb9bbc.jpg\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"366\" src=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/b7f9a09a7e0972b561507406efeb9bbc.jpg\" title=\"Break the fukcing great fire wall you will reach the truth #fuckGFW\" width=\"348\" /></a></p>\n<p>接下来是<span>MAC</span>平台的VPN设置方法：</p>\n<p>1. 打开Mac的联网设置</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/11.png\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"343\" src=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/11.png\" title=\"1\" width=\"550\" /></a></p>\n<p>2. 然后点右边的加号，添加新的连接，选择添加VPN，模式是PPTP。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/21.png\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"439\" src=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/21.png\" title=\"2\" width=\"550\" /></a></p>\n<p>3. 输入购买的VPN的服务器地址，帐号以及密码。然后确认。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/31.png\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"453\" src=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/31.png\" title=\"3\" width=\"550\" /></a></p>\n<p>4. 然后点击连接，VPN就设置好了。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/41.png\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"343\" src=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/41.png\" title=\"4\" width=\"550\" /></a></p>\n<p>5. 如果你想要你的VPN全局接管你的互联网通信。你还需要做如下设置。<br /> 在Send all traffic over VPN connection那选中打钩。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/51.png\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"395\" src=\"https://sthoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/51.png\" title=\"5\" width=\"550\" /></a></p>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n<p> </p>\n<div>敬请订阅中国数字时代中文版（http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/feed），阅读最有价值的中文信息。下载TOR等翻墙软件，请访问Sesawe(http://fanqianggongju.info/)。需翻墙？请发电邮(最好用Gmail)到:CDTcaonima@gmail.com。GFW Blog订阅地址：http://feeds2.feedburner.com/chinagfwblog<img alt=\"\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5500297126185736776-5813076366